text: I loved the first one and finally got to see the second one. It was another great message that I believe in whole heartedly. Don't work yourself to death and just enjoy the time you have with your kids in simple ways. Life is too short to be MISERABLE over petty competition. I will always be PROUD to be a Bad Mom. It means a life filled with REALITY which equals HAPPINESS. Since no one is going to make it out of here alive, over achieving is ultimately MEDIOCRE. I see family life as nothing more than what the ants do, we create our young, build our homes and work to collect food. Why go against the grain of what the natural world is because of other people's IGNORANT opinions?
